spec_data.Name: python-peak-util-symbols
spec_data.Description:
SymbolType gives you access to the peak.util.symbols module, previously
available only by installing the full PEAK toolkit. peak.util.symbols provides
a Symbol type and two built-in symbols that are used by PEAK: NOT_FOUND and
NOT_GIVEN.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 02:45:55 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Simple "symbol" type, useful for enumerations or sentinels
